cs.GT, cs.CR, cs.DS, cs.CC, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.GT (Game Theory): The paper proposes a combinatorial auction mechanism for cloud resource allocation, which involves game theory and mechanism design. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security): The paper addresses the issue of bid privacy in cloud auctions and proposes a differentially private mechanism to protect users' privacy. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper discusses the computational complexity of the proposed mechanisms and their running time. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity): The paper analyzes the computational complexity of the proposed mechanisms and their running time. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper employs the exponential mechanism, a widely used technique in AI and machine learning, to compute the clearing unit price vector.
